High Score

Primary Actor: Player

Scenario

Player double clicks the game icon in desktop. Then game opens. Player chooses “High Score” on the main menu. Player opens the “High Score” section. If player wants to go back to the main menu, player presses “Go Back” button.

Description

Player opens the game and main menu will be loaded. Then player goes to the “High Score” screen. High scores handled by High Score
Manager. High Score Manager get the data from the File Manager and it gets graphics from Window, then renders the screen, so that 
player can see the high scores. If player wants to go back, it also handled by High Score Manager, presses go back button to return 
to the main menu.
